    "The relevant application directions are categorized according to the requirements for model generation or comprehension.",
    "RALM on NLG indicates that the accomplishment of the task primarily depends on the generative capabilities.",
    "Conversely, RALM on NLU indicates that the accomplishment of the task primarily depends on the comprehension capabilities.",
    "Finally, RALM on both NLU and NLG indicates that the task is generally handled in two ways, one that relies primarily on comprehension capabilities and one that relies primarily on generative capabilities.",
    "Figure 6 illustrates the categorization of applications."
